import MyInput from './Components/Input'
import MyButton from './Components/Button'
import { Container, Content, Row, Column } from "./style";

const App = () => {
  return (
    <Container >
      <Content>
        <MyInput />

        <Row>
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
        </Row>

        <Row>
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
        </Row>

        <Row>
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
          <MyButton />
        </Row>

      </Content>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default App;
